{"tid":659624,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"蹲就蹲啦 SQUAT 乜尻亞洲蹲呀","createTime":"2018-05-10T04:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T11:11:38.000Z","uid":125111,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce9671cd0fbf09c3636559df1175fc2f6ec6317","tid":659624,"uid":125111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"明明 蹲 /squat 得低係人類 無分種族都應該要做到<br />\n或者可以講成bb仔 小朋友可以做到<br />\n<br />\nsquat 得低有好多要素<br />\n最重要係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. flexibility 柔軟度 + mobility 活動幅度（包括knee, ankle, hip... 等等）<br />\n<br />\n點解d人squat唔低<br />\n因為都市人 打工狗 日撚日坐 對電腦<br />\n肌肉不平衡咩引致 flexibility + mobility 不足囉屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東張西望真係好q垃圾 乜野亞洲蹲都要報<br />\n搞到個個都意為 Squat = Asian專利<br />\n<br />\n比d有squat開有知識既鬼佬見到真係又笑尻你<br />\n蹲得低係對人體好多好處 <br />\n亦等同你冇乜太大肌肉不平衡問題<br />\n相對黎講 肌肉痛症亦都少d<br />\n肌力夠有做gym 心血管同病緊係少啦<br />\n<br />\n但唔係叫亞洲蹲囉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/115949_afbd97211fc0566010371740ee104287.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F115949_afbd97211fc0566010371740ee104287.png&h=7bc86bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/120005_9843e2033c2b5bb680b6e9713c3b57cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F120005_9843e2033c2b5bb680b6e9713c3b57cb.png&h=b85c0a09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0594c37f87d16e214bc83a5af6242650d24f927","tid":659624,"uid":77569,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:02:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53547f2ed510d0df19eb166fa92fa1d870bb4fc3","tid":659624,"uid":125111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e0594c37f87d16e214bc83a5af6242650d24f92